# zPriority

**Instance Property**

The relative importance of the annotation view when in an unselected state with respect to its ordering along the z-axis.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var zPriority: MKAnnotationViewZPriority { get set }
```

## Discussion

The constant [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKAnnotationViewZPriority/defaultUnselected] is the default value for [doc://com.apple.mapkit/documentation/MapKit/MKAnnotationView/zPriority].

## Setting the priority for display

- **displayPriority**: The display priority of the annotation view.
- **MKFeatureDisplayPriority**: Constants that indicates the display priority for annotations.
- **selectedZPriority**: The relative importance of the annotation view when in a selected state with respect to its ordering along the z-axis.
- **MKAnnotationViewZPriority**: Constants that indicates the priority for ordering overlapping annotation views.
